      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "So let us discern for ourselves what is right;\n\tlet us learn together
        what is good.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "For Job also said, \u2018I am innocent,\n\tbut God has taken away
        my rights.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "I am innocent, but they call me a liar.\n\tMy suffering is incurable,
        though I have not sinned.\u2019  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "\u201CTell me, has there ever been a man like Job,\n\twith his thirst
        for irreverent talk?  "
      comments: []
